From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|warm|lang=enm}}, {{term|werm|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|wearm|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{recons|warmaz|lang=gem-pro}}, with different proposed origins:
